# Scenario: No Link header on any prior response; agent falls back to /.well-known/agent-catalog.json.
# Expected outcome: agent fetches /.well-known/agent-catalog.json from the origin.

### Initial request
GET https://example.com/some/page HTTP/1.1
Accept: text/html

### Response (no Link header)
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: text/html

<html>...</html>

### Agent fallback request
GET https://example.com/.well-known/agent-catalog.json HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json
